GNU/Hex
=====
this system has flexible configuration of both packages, file systems, and the kernel itself.
you will essentially write the code for this system yourself, customizing it the way you need.
the project is inspired by the GNU/Linux ideology and is promoted on Netwide Assembly x86.

source at src/
documentation at docs/
other files at storage/

